column3:
<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
The allergic Yok Huy is in need of a dry delivery.
Gather Larh Tortoh violets and defeat any threats that appear.
Deliver the Larh Tortoh violets to the allergic Yok Huy.
Ah, I know you! You are a member of the Third Promise's retinue, as I recall, and strong for your size besides.
I would ask a favor, then. Could you pick three Larh Tortoh violets and bring them to me?
The field's monstrous plants and their pollen are more than my nose can bear, and no one wants drippy flowers. At the very least, <Emphasis>I</Emphasis> do not.
I need three of those violets that grow in Larh Tortoh. You will fetch them for me, won't you? Please, spare my poor nose...
Welcome back! The picking went well, I take it?
Thank you for obliging me. I wanted to get flowers for my grandmother, and these are one of her favorites.
We have a tradition of carving symbols of our favorite things on our graves, you see. Hers has a flower for each of the four seasons, so I've been giving her a few of each throughout the year.
Well, I had better get these to Grandmother before they wilt. Take this as a token of my thanks!
